Package com.millicast

Class Subscriber

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.millicast.Client
      • com.millicast.Subscriber
  • public class Subscriber
extends Client
    The Subscriber class. Its purpose is to receive media by subscribing to a millicast stream. The stream must already exists and someone must publish media.
